ing binaries, or other false positives, as well as\nto conduct detailed transit observations with facilities like JWST or HST.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jul 2018 17:05:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Dec 2018 14:53:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-27"}
