munication. In particular, the solar-powered UAV first climbs up to a high\naltitude to harvest a sufficient amount of solar energy and then descents again\nto a lower altitude to reduce the path loss of the communication links to the\nusers it serves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jul 2018 22:47:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-02"}
